[v2-operation]: https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/main/versions/2.0.md#operation-object
[v3-operation]: https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/3.0.3/versions/3.0.3.md#operation-object

