| `links` (OAS3)           |                                                     | Not currently supported.                            |

```typespec
@get op read(@path id: string): {
  /** the widget */
  @body
  widget: Widget;

  @header xRateLimitRemaining: int32;
  @header xRateLimitReset: int32;
